  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThe guides on Hibernate with Panache don't have an example on how to load lazy associations.\r\nThis might be problematic for people trying it for the first time because the will have a LazyInitializationException when returning the JSON response with Resteasy.\r\n\r\nWe should show some examples on how to do joins and how to load collections eagerly when needed.\r\nThis is more important for Hibernate Reactive because collections must be loaded using an explicit call to `.fetch`.\r\n\r\nThis is about updating the documentation only.\r\n",
